- 폰트의 이름 또는 저작권 정보를 변경하여 배포하는 행위  

The following actions are strictly prohibited:  
- Modifying, altering, reverse-engineering, decompiling, or extracting any part of the font file (Hungeul.otf)  
- Redistributing, reselling, or rehosting the font file on any other websites, apps, or software packages  
- Changing the font name or copyright notice and redistributing it

